<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="MTA98">
<l>poṉṟikaḻu mēṉip puricaṭaiyam puṇṇiyaṉu</l>
<l>niṉṟulakan tāya neṭumālu – meṉṟu</l>
<l>miruvaraṅkat tāṟṟiriva rēlu moruva</l>
<l>ṉoruvaṉaṅkat teṉṟu muḷaṉ</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The body glittering with gold: the virtuous one with matted locks</l>
<l>and tall Māl who constantly extends the world, even if</l>
<l>they always wander around with a body of two, always</l>
<l>one is present in the body of the other.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
